txt.en: Your mission is to defeat Rúnar Wolfstooth and put an end to the Dourhand expedition into the depths of Kidzul-kâlah.
After defeating Rúnar Wolfstooth, a tremor has coursed through the depths of Kidzul-kâlah. Is this some unseen doing of the Dourhands?

A Dourhand expedition has descended into the newly-drained depths of Kidzul-kâlah seeking to claim its riches for their own.
